# CPUC Network Test Parser
====================================

CSIT project at CSUMB, focused on improving previous work of a Python-based Network Test parser, with an emphasis on simplicity for use on a server.

This code was "forked" from my previous project at https://github.com/pwalker91/CPUC--iPerfParser_with_DB_Storage. This was forked after the November 1st, 2014 Commit.

## Please refer to Documentation webpage for more information.
http://pwalker91.github.io/CSUMB_CalSPEED_Parser/ProjectDocumentation.html
